posting_body: TRANSFORMATION IN PROGRESS > UPGRADES & UPDATES COMING SOON!
Franklin Park is not only conveniently located, but it also provides amazing amenities to all its residents.
In-home features include a fully-equipped kitchen appliance package, open & spacious floor plan layouts, additional storage area, walk-in closet(s) AND a private patio or balcony space!

We want our residents to be proud of their home, which is why we’ve also included stellar community amenities which include, but are not limited to, a beautiful community clubhouse, planned resident activities & more.
Franklin Park offers two, three & four bedroom apartment homes that you’ll undoubtedly fall in love with.
The amenities and location here are unbeatable.
Call today to schedule a personal tour and sign your lease today!
